Are there samples on

(1) How to generate a 270 edi file using only the OopFactory.X12.Hipaa.Eligibility objects.

(2) How to parse a 271 in edi format to the OopFactory.X12.Hipaa.Eligibility objects.

I don't have any code to do #1.

You can look in the unit test assembly OopFactory.X12.Hipaa.Tests.Unit and look at the Eligibiity.BenefitResponseTester clasee to see how to turn the 271 into the objects.
